OL,3,CWelsh Rugby Union makes announcement
OL,4,Cover future of four regions
OL,6,FThe Welsh Rugby Union has announced it
OL,7,Fwill move away from a model of four
OL,8,Fevenly funded clubs after Ospreys and
OL,9,FScarlets did not sign up to its new
OL,10,FProfessional Rugby Agreement.
OL,12,FThe agreement (PRA25) had been signed
OL,13,Fby Dragons and Cardiff, who were last
OL,14,Fmonth taken over by the WRU having
OL,15,Fserved formal notification that they
OL,16,Fintended to enter administration.
