OL,4,Cover future of four regions
OL,6,FLast week Ospreys and Scarlets said
OL,7,Fthey had asked the WRU for assurances
OL,8,Fthat the takeover "will not
OL,9,Fdisproportionally benefit Cardiff and
OL,10,Fdisadvantage the independent clubs",
OL,11,Fadding: "Until we have greater
OL,12,Fclarity, we are currently unable to
OL,13,Fsign the PRA25."
