OL,3,CWelsh Rugby Union makes announcement
OL,4,Cover future of four regions
OL,6,FOn Sunday, the WRU released a
OL,7,Fstatement saying that with those clubs
OL,8,Fnot signing by the deadline set, it
OL,9,Fhad therefore taken the "difficult but
OL,10,Fnecessary decision to issue the formal
OL,11,Ftwo-year notice to terminate the
OL,12,Fcurrent PRA agreement in order, in
OL,13,Fparticular, to proceed with its debt
OL,14,Frefinancing."
OL,16,FThe statement continued: "The One
OL,17,FWales Strategy (unveiled in June last
OL,18,Fyear) was designed to create a more
OL,19,Faligned, financially sustainable and
OL,20,Fcompetitive future for professional
OL,21,Frugby across Wales.
OL,26,@qD@YOUvD@MO]xD@ZOU
