OL,3,CWelsh Rugby Union makes announcement
OL,4,Cover future of four regions
OL,6,F"The WRU's preference from the outset
OL,7,Fwas to maintain four professional
OL,8,Fclubs (on equal funding) within this
OL,9,Fframework. Everyone worked hard to
OL,10,Fachieve that. However, agreement on
OL,11,Fthe new PRA25 could not be reached
OL,12,Fwith two of the professional clubs.
OL,14,F"This is not a decision that was taken
OL,15,Flightly, however given the WRU's
OL,16,Fduties to the game in Wales as a
OL,17,Fwhole, the broader performance,
OL,18,Ffinancial and strategic needs of the
OL,19,Fgame must take precedence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
