OL,3,CWelsh Rugby Union makes announcement
OL,4,Cover future of four regions
OL,6,F"In practical terms, the WRU will work
OL,7,Fclosely with all four professional
OL,8,Fclubs to agree the way forward beyond
OL,9,FJune 2027, with an open mind to all
OL,10,Fconstructive and realistic proposals.
OL,12,F"That said, given the seismic changes
OL,13,Fin the rugby landscape since we first
OL,14,Fstarted negotiating PRA25, the system
OL,15,Fwill not return to the model of four
OL,16,Fevenly funded clubs."
