OL,3,CWelsh Rugby Union makes announcement
OL,4,Cover future of four regions
OL,6,FThe announcement comes after reports
OL,7,Fthat one of the four regional teams
OL,8,Fwould be cut under the new plans,
OL,9,Fsomething neither confirmed nor denied
OL,10,Fby the WRU.
OL,12,FWRU chief executive Abi Tierney said:
OL,13,F"We are continuing to talk to all four
OL,14,Fclubs about what the future will hold.
OL,16,F"We recognise this will be time of
OL,17,Funcertainty and are committed to
OL,18,Ftreating all the clubs, players, and
OL,19,Fsupporters with respect and fairness
OL,20,Fthroughout this process.
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@AOU
