OL,3,CWelsh Rugby Union makes announcement
OL,4,Cover future of four regions
OL,6,F"We acknowledge the continued
OL,7,Fcommitment of each club to Welsh rugby
OL,8,Fand will formulate a new plan with the
OL,9,Fbest interests of the whole game in
OL,10,FWales at the forefront of our thinking.
OL,12,F"When I announced the headline
OL,13,Fstrategy back in July 2024, I said one
OL,14,Fthing is for certain, given the
OL,15,Fchallenges facing rugby in Wales and
OL,16,Fglobally, there will be times when we
OL,17,Fneed to adjust our course. We must
OL,18,Fseize this opportunity."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@XO]
