OL,3,CWelsh Rugby Union makes announcement
OL,4,Cover future of four regions
OL,6,FProfessional Rugby Board chair Malcolm
OL,7,FWall said: "The next phase of
OL,8,Fconsultation, as always, will be
OL,9,Fconducted with the best interests of
OL,10,Fthe whole of Welsh rugby at its heart."
OL,12,FIn a joint statement, Ospreys and
OL,13,FScarlets expressed concern and
OL,14,Fdisappointment at the WRU's position,
OL,15,Fcalling for more "clarity and detail"
OL,16,Fwhich allows for continued growth.
