OL,4,Cover future of four regions
OL,6,F"This U-turn has now created more
OL,7,Fdestabilising and debilitating
OL,8,Funcertainty in our game, with
OL,9,Fpertinent questions being asked by
OL,10,Fstakeholders across our clubs and
OL,11,Fwithin our communities regarding the
OL,12,Ffuture framework and landscape for
OL,13,Fprofessional rugby in Wales," the
OL,14,Fstatement from the clubs read.
